description: Pizza Block: Where humor, and cryptocurrency converge. Indulge in a mouthwatering collection of NFTs inscribed on exotic 'pizza' Sats from the historic Pizza Transaction of May 22, 2010. Created by the talented artist @Presage0007, each NFT is a pizza-themed jokes that will leave you craving for more. Join this exclusive community of pizza enthusiasts and collectors, and celebrate the delightful fusion of laughter and the legacy of Bitcoin.
name: Pizza Block
